                <p>
                    <milestone n="1" unit="line"/>
 The 8th year of the Emperor Caesar Titus Aelius Hadrianus Antoninus Augustus Pius. 
                    <milestone n="3" unit="line"/>
Panesneus, son of Horus and Tamarieus and grandson of Panesneus, has worked on the dykes (m. 2) from Pauni 17-21 in the same 8th year 
                    <milestone n="5" unit="line"/>
on the canal Psinaleitis at Theadelphia. <milestone n="8" unit="line"/>Statement (m. 3) signed by - - -, in charge of the seeding.
                <lb/>
                <note>Translation: A.C. Johnson, Roman Egypt (1936) no. 6</note>
            </p>
        </div>
